Hello,

for Docker please run 'docker-compose up'.
for pytest please run 'pytest'
For Heroku please follow https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/container-registry-and-runtime:
    heroku login
    heroku container:login
    #heroku create
    heroku container:push web -a secure-spire-80562 (rabbit-reader-03)
    heroku container:release web -a secure-spire-80562 (rabbit-reader-03)
    heroku open

Have fun ;)